songs.title: ​gods of the city!
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: Keyon Christ]
(wordless singing)

[Chorus 1: Alicia Williams]
Maybe we can be the gods of the city, yeah
Maybe we can be the gods of the city
Maybe we can be the gods of the city, yeah
Maybe we can be the gods of the city

[Verse 1: Glenn Travis]
I skrrt 'round the city like "woah"
In a Ferrari, like fuck everybody
Man this shit can never get old
Fire, fire, fire, fire, fire
Burning baby
Burn into the morning won't you
Come and take me home and show me
That you ain't scared of me
Baby, come to me
Baby, show me that you know

[Chorus 2: All]
We can be the gods of the city yeah
We can be the gods of the city

[Outro: Anthony Flammia & Glenn Travis]
We could be the gods of the city
We could be the gods of the city
We could be the gods of the city
We could be the gods...
We could be the gods of the city
We could be the gods of the city
We could be the gods of the city
I'm a god
Just like that...
